Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before moving to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time difference between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Minimum time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Closed' in the most frequent process variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases that exceed the average case duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Longest time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to any 'Completed' activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Accepted + Assigned' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and its impact on case duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases with above-average performance in reaching 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved' compared to 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
